  "notes": "And they're all built on common foundations to scale AI transformation safely and reliably. \n\nWith native mirroring to OneLake, all your data is available in our scalable, unified data lake, providing a single point to discover and explore your data. With OneLake storing your data in an open format, it unifies your  operational, analytical, structured and unstructured data in one open, connected foundation.  You get a delta lake version of your data with No ETL copy and no cost for the storage – a great way to integrate seamlessly into your existing unified data estate or jumpstart one if you don’t have one already.\n\nYou've also got native AI capabilities like semantic retrieval and agentic memory, plus model integration, and you've got real-time integrations with Fabric RTI (Real Time Intelligence) and Microsoft Foundry."
